<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-consideration-of-for">in consideration of / for</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>考虑到；由于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mobile phones must be switched off inside the castle in consideration of other visitors.
考虑到其他游客，在城堡内要关闭手机。</p><footer>2010 天津改</footer></div></div>